>"Thanks for teh info Legacy" Said the female by 
>comlink  "We will be ready for everyone" 

Legacy nodded to himself as he keyed a few other controls, and a few more lights from a few other systems began to glow, giving the surrounding room an almost erie appearance. 

"Acknowledged Unit Talon" Legacy spoke over the comlink as he continued to examine his own sensor logs. "However I still require a situation report. Are you currently under attack and do you require assistance?"
